mais la vrm ça me fout la rage c des gros trimard c pas possible

battered with indifference
and callous rage
by fake deluded charlatan
spouting noxious lies non-stop
no sense of the truth except yours
yr denials wearing thin 
as reality sets in
We the People has spoken
your time is up
